# List of monuments in Floriana

This is a list of monuments in Floriana, Malta, which are listed on the National Inventory of the Cultural Property of the Maltese Islands., as well as Grade 1 scheduled properties from the [https://www.pa.org.mt/en/scheduled Malta Scheduled Property Register] maintained by Malta's Planning Authority. The latter are denoted by an ID beginning with the letters MSPR.
